<!-- WHY JOIN -->

<section class="why" id="why">
  <div class="section-label"><span>Why Serve</span></div>
  <h2 class="section-heading">THE BENEFITS OF<br><span>MILITARY SERVICE</span></h2>
  <div class="why-intro">
    <p class="why-body">Military service provides unmatched opportunities for personal growth, financial stability, career advancement, and lifelong brotherhood. Here's what awaits you.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="benefits-grid">
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🎓</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Full Education Benefits</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">The GI Bill covers 100% of tuition at in-state public universities. Additional funding available for trade schools, online programs, and graduate degrees.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">Up to $28,000/yr</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🏥</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Healthcare Coverage</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">Comprehensive medical, dental, and vision coverage for you and your family — at no cost while on active duty. TRICARE coverage available post-service.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">Full Family Coverage</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">💰</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Competitive Pay</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">Base pay, housing allowance (BAH), food allowance (BAS), and specialty pay combine for a competitive total compensation package that grows with rank.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">+ Housing & Food</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🏠</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Housing & Relocation</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">On-base housing or monthly housing allowance provided. Moving expenses covered with each PCS (Permanent Change of Station) assignment.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">BAH Included</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">✈️</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">World Travel</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">Deploy and serve across 30+ countries. Space-available military flights let you and your family travel the world at little to no cost.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">Global Assignments</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">📈</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Retirement & Pension</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">Retire after 20 years of service with a monthly pension for life. The Blended Retirement System (BRS) also includes a 401(k)-style TSP contribution.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">Pension for Life</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🤝</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Leadership Training</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">World-class leadership development from day one. Skills you'll use for a lifetime — in uniform and in your civilian career.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">Transferable Skills</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🛡️</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Job Security</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">Guaranteed employment, stable income regardless of economic conditions, and a clear promotion pathway based on merit and performance.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">Guaranteed Employment</span>
    </div>
    <div class="benefit-card">
      <div class="benefit-icon">🌍</div>
      <div class="benefit-title">Purpose & Brotherhood</div>
      <div class="benefit-desc">Join a community of men and women bound by honor and sacrifice. The bonds forged in service last a lifetime. You'll never be alone.</div>
      <span class="benefit-tag">Lifelong Community</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

